Package environment.model.locations

This module contains all the classes necessary for modelling the different locations of the petrol station.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Location
    This abstract class encapsulates the behaviour of a location in the Station.
    Pump
    Place where RoadUsers will fill up their vehicles
    ShoppingArea
    Place where a Road user is going to wait.
    TestLocation
    This is the test class for Location, It tests the: Location.enter(RoadUser) Location.returnToQueue(RoadUser) Location.clone() All test classes for the subclasses of Location must extend from this.
    TestPump
    Tests Pump.
    TestShoppingArea
    Tests ShoppingArea.
    TestTill
    Tests Till.
    Till
    Place where a RoadUser pays for the transaction.

Package environment.model.locations Description

This module contains all the classes necessary for modelling the different locations of the petrol station.
